OL,7,FMPs will quiz the BBC chairman, Samir
OL,8,FShah, and two other key figures on
OL,9,FMonday amid concerns around the
OL,10,Fbroadcaster's impartiality following
OL,11,Fthe editing of a speech on Panorama.
OL,13,FFormer editorial adviser Michael
OL,14,FPrescott, who raised concerns that a
OL,15,FPanorama episode included selective
OL,16,Fediting of a speech made by President
OL,17,FDonald Trump before the attack on the
OL,18,FUS Capitol in 2021, is one of those
OL,19,Ffacing questions from MPs on the Media
OL,20,Fand Sport Committee.
