OL,3,CBBC bosses, including chair Samir
OL,4,CShah, to be quizzed on impartiality by
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FThey will be quizzed on the BBC's
OL,8,Feditorial standards guidelines and how
OL,9,Fthe corporation complies during the
OL,10,Fevidence sessions, which will begin at
OL,11,F3.30pm on Monday.
OL,13,FThe committee wrote to the BBC to ask
OL,14,Fabout action being taken after a
OL,15,Freport by Mr Prescott raised concerns
OL,16,Fthat a Panorama episode included
OL,17,Fselective editing of a speech made by
OL,18,FPresident Donald Trump before the
OL,19,Fattack on the US Capitol in 2021.
