OL,7,FBBC director-general Tim Davie and
OL,8,Fnews chief Deborah Turness resigned in
OL,9,Fthe fallout from the report becoming
OL,10,Fpublic, while Mr Shah apologised on
OL,11,Fbehalf of the BBC over an "error of
OL,12,Fjudgment" and accepted that the
OL,13,Fediting of the 2024 documentary gave
OL,14,F"the impression of a direct call for
OL,15,Fviolent action".
