OL,4,CShah, to be quizzed on impartiality by
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FIn response to Mr Trump's threat, a
OL,8,FBBC spokesperson said: "We have had no
OL,9,Ffurther contact from President Trump's
OL,10,Flawyers at this point. Our position
OL,11,Fremains the same."
OL,13,FSir Robbie, a former senior
OL,14,FConservative Party adviser, has faced
OL,15,Fcalls for his removal from the BBC
OL,16,Fboard, with creative industries union
OL,17,FBectu saying his position was
OL,18,F"untenable".
